message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with the task of Visual Question Answering (VQA) which involves processing data with both visual and linguistic processing. This task is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses deep learning models (cs.LG) and their performance over VQA datasets. Additionally, the paper involves analysis and future research directions (cs.IR) related to VQA.
